00:28.821 --> 00:31.238
Took a whole lot of tryin'

00:31.376 --> 00:33.964
Just to get up that hill

00:34.103 --> 00:36.519
Now we're up
in the big leagues

00:36.657 --> 00:39.108
Gettin' our turn at bat

00:39.246 --> 00:41.593
